title: Ritz-Carlton To Unveil First Golf Resort In China
text:
Published By: Fastlane Magazine - Today 
The Ritz-Carlton Hotel Company has unveiled plans for its first golf resort in China when The Ritz-Carlton, Mission Hills opens in late 2015...
